# cdpartners Component

**Purpose**: Displays a grid of partner logos with optional title and subtitle, linking to external partner sites.

**Variants**:
- Default
- xDemo

**CMS Fields**:
- "title" (string)
- "subtitle" (string)
- "partnerLogos" (array of objects each with partnerName, link, image)
- "selectableVariant" (string)

**Usage**: 
Import this component from "cdpartners" or from the dynamic page loading. 
In the CMS, add the "cdpartners" item to "components" and configure partner logos.